  "verse": [
    "Shadows crawling up the wall\nHear the demon's call\nBlood and fire in the night\nMetal burning bright",
    "Chains of fate are pulling tight\nFighting with all my might\nNo redemption, no remorse\nFollowing this darkened course",
    "Riffs of thunder, drums of war\nMetal forevermore\nScreaming into endless void\nAll joy destroyed",
    "Raging against the dying light\nFighting through the night\nHeavy metal in my veins\nBreaking all the chains",
    "Iron fist and steel will\nClimbing up this hill\nBlood and sweat and endless tears\nConquering all fears"
  ],
  "verse_alt": [
